<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .proposal-title {
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .cta-link {
            display: inline-block;
            margin: 8px 0 20px;
            color: #0066cc;
            word-break: break-all;
        }
        .comment-block {
            background: #f5f5f5;
            border-left: 3px solid #ccc;
            padding: 8px 12px;
            margin: 8px 0;
            font-style: italic;
        }
        .divider {
            border: none;
            border-top: 2px solid #ddd;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
        .lang-label {
            font-size: 0.75em;
            color: #999;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.1em;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    {% set call_title = object.call.title if object.call else '' %}
    {% set reviewer_name = review.reviewer.username if review.reviewer else '' %}
    {% set status_de = {'approved': 'Angenommen', 'rejected': 'Abgelehnt', 'revise': 'Überarbeitung erbeten'}.get(review.status, review.status) %}
    {% set status_en = {'approved': 'Approved', 'rejected': 'Rejected', 'revise': 'Revision requested'}.get(review.status, review.status) %}

    <p class="lang-label">Deutsch</p>

    <p>Ein Gutachten ist eingegangen für die Einreichung <span class="proposal-title">"{{ object.title }}"</span>{% if call_title %} in <span class="proposal-title">"{{ call_title }}"</span>{% endif %}.</p>

    <p><strong>Gutachter:</strong> {{ reviewer_name }}<br>
    <strong>Ergebnis:</strong> {{ status_de }}</p>

    {% if review.comment %}
    <div class="comment-block">{{ review.comment }}</div>
    {% endif %}

    <p>Die Einreichung ist unter folgendem Link einsehbar:</p>

    <a class="cta-link" href="{{ proposal_url }}">{{ proposal_url }}</a>

    <hr class="divider">

    <p class="lang-label">English</p>

    <p>A review has been submitted for the submission <span class="proposal-title">"{{ object.title }}"</span>{% if call_title %} in <span class="proposal-title">"{{ call_title }}"</span>{% endif %}.</p>

    <p><strong>Reviewer:</strong> {{ reviewer_name }}<br>
    <strong>Result:</strong> {{ status_en }}</p>

    {% if review.comment %}
    <div class="comment-block">{{ review.comment }}</div>
    {% endif %}

    <p>The submission can be viewed at the following link:</p>

    <a class="cta-link" href="{{ proposal_url }}">{{ proposal_url }}</a>
</body>
</html>
